Subject:	CardConnect Costs

Hey Jared.	..here is a summary of the various components re: CardConnect direct costs:

•	CardConnect (CC) Gateway Operations Costs: ~$3,284/mo.
	o This is for 2 gateway instances (production + failover) ...and is mostly comprised of bandwidth usage
•	Litle (Vantiv) Platform and Settlement Costs
	o Per Item Fees to Litle = $0.01/auth for credit + $0.015/settlement for credit ($0.025/item total)
	o	Settlement of Discover to CC Costs = $50/mo.
	o	Settlement of Amex to CC Costs = $0.15%
	o Plus the $0.025/item and the basis points on Amex from above, our total Vantiv invoices ranged from $36k to $60k per month
…	with recent volumes trending up ~5-10%/mo.
NOTE: CC indicated on our call this week they may be able to SQUEEZE some additional cost savings from Vantiv
•	Tokenization Costs
	o	CC Tokenization = $500/mo.
	o Payeezy Tokenization *(for app-based businesses) = $1,500/mo.
•	3rd Party Costs
	o	Cardinal Centinel = $1,000/mo.
•	Datacenter Costs
	o Datacenter costs *(cages, racks, power, ac, monitoring, ﬁrewalls, etc.) = $2,500/mo.

Thanks…
-randy
